      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DOLLY'S MY MUM (8) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from five tries. Below best last time at Murray Bridge (26.07) in a Grade 6, finishing a 3 length fourth. Expected to go close. DIMORA BLUEY (5) is a talented type who notched his 8th career success when too good (19.88) at Angle Park last time. The form from his last run stacks up well. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. ROCKLEA EARLE (1) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (25.99) from Box 1 at Murray Bridge. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Expected to be in the finish again. COMPTON FRANKY (2) drops in journey and can play a major role.",
